    • Method Detail

      • add

        public void add(GameObject object)
        Adds specified GameObject to list of GameObjects, which is used for drawing. The index in the list determines in which order GameObjects are drawn on the canvas: Smallest index == drawn first (under all others) Largest index == drawn last (on top of all others)
        Parameters:
        object - GameObject to be added to list

      • draw

        public void draw()
        Draws background and all GameObjects on the canvas.
